*Pisao* je o tome u svojoj knjizi. (He wrote about it in his book.)

Učenici su *pisali* o nečemu što je ona rekla. (The students wrote about something that she said.)

Ona je *pisala* knjigu za decu. (She wrote a book for children.)

*Pisanje* je bilo veoma zabavno. (Writing was very fun.)

Oni su *pisali* lepe pesme. (They wrote beautiful songs.)